Anita Garvin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anita_Garvin 0 Anita Garvin (February 11, 1907 – July 7, 1994) was an American actress and comedian who appeared in both silent and sound films. She is best known for her work with comedians Laurel and Hardy and Charley Chase.
